                <mxCell id="title" value="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 34px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(17, 24, 39);&quot;&gt;Bupa As One Target State Architecture&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 17px; color: rgb(55, 65, 81); margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;High-level enterprise architecture view: shared platforms, reusable services and governed fulfilment behind one Bupa experience&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
