                <mxCell id="decision-footer" value="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(17, 24, 39);&quot;&gt;Architecture decision test&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 13px; color: rgb(17, 24, 39); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.45;&quot;&gt;Strategic initiatives should land in this stack: use shared foundations, publish contracts, reuse capability services, feed governed data and keep BU fulfilment behind adapters. Exceptions are allowed only with an owner, rationale and convergence path.&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fillColor=#FFF7ED;strokeColor=#F97316;strokeWidth=2;arcSize=6;" parent="1" vertex="1">
